@startuml FrontendArchitecture
!theme plain

title Frontend Architecture — SPA Layered Design

skinparam rectangle {
    BorderColor #333
}

rectangle "Presentation Layer" as Pres #FFCCCC {
    rectangle "Pages /
Route Components" as Pages
    rectangle "UI Components
(Ant Design / Quasar)" as UI
    rectangle "Composable /
Hooks (Vue3 / React)" as Hooks
}

rectangle "Application Layer" as App #FFFFCC {
    rectangle "ViewModels /
State Stores (Pinia)" as VM
    rectangle "UseCase
Facades" as Facades
    rectangle "DTOs &
Validation" as DTO
}

rectangle "Infrastructure Layer" as Infra #CCFFCC {
    rectangle "API Client
(axios / fetch)" as API
    rectangle "Auth Adapter
(JWT / OAuth)" as Auth
    rectangle "WS/Realtime
(Socket.IO)" as WS
}

rectangle "Domain (Shared)" as Domain #CCCCFF {
    rectangle "Entity
Models" as Entity
    rectangle "Value
Objects" as VO
    rectangle "Domain
Event Handlers" as DE
}

pages --> UI : renders
pages --> Hooks : uses
UI --> VM : binds state
Hooks --> VM : reads/writes
VM --> Facades : calls
Facades --> DTO : transforms
Facades --> API : request
Facades --> Auth : token
Facades --> WS : subscribe
API --> DTO : deserializes
Domain --> Entity : models
Domain --> VO : models
Domain --> DE : handles

note right of Pages
  **Presentation Rules**
  1. Must stay "dumb" — only
     display UI and delegate.
  2. No direct API calls.
  3. Use composition for
     shared behavior.
end note

note right of Facades
  **UseCase Facades**
  Orchestrate side effects:
  - API request
  - Error mapping
  - Loading state
  - Cache invalidation
end note

note right of API
  **API Client Config**
  - Base URL from env
  - Request/Response interceptors
  - MDC header injection:
    X-Correlation-Id
  - Retry + circuit breaker
end note

legend right
  | Color | Layer |
  | #FFCCCC | Presentation |
  | #FFFFCC | Application |
  | #CCFFCC | Infrastructure |
  | #CCCCFF | Domain |
endlegend

@enduml
